      "raw_text": "The Northern Pacific will continue\nthe Sunday excursions to st. Maries.\nFerrelIs and st. Joe during the sum-\nmer. Train will leave Spokane 8 a\nm. for Occur d'Alene. Steamer Cakes\nleaving there on arrival of train for\na delightful ride across the lake and\nTN the St. Joe river. arriving at Fer\nrelrs about p m, where stop OF\n30 minutes will be made for dinner\nThose preferring to d. 10 can take\nlunch baskets and eas lunch on the\nboat. Returning train will arrive\nSpokane about p. m. Fare for the\nround trip 81."
